author: Insta360
description:
Antigravity A1 has landed!

Featuring an 8K 360 camera, Antigravity A1 comes ready to make every flight a moment to remember.

✅ 360 Immersive Flight
✅ Fly first, frame later with 8K 360 degree capture
✅ Just 249g for maximum compatibility
✅ Dual 1-inch micro-OLED Vision Goggles displays for a truly immersive experience
✅ Two types of motion control, fly on instinct with FreeMotion Mode or FPV Mode
✅ 24/39 Mins battery options 
✅ Auto Editing

Discover more: https://tinyurl.com/36j3fr8s
